{"_id":"f4d7a85120d8eca0","name":"Table 1 The Emissary","description":"<h2>The Emissary</h2><p>The Children of the Song: Bear in mind that the death of the Messenger Emissary changes much on Coriolis.</p><p>The Spider’s Web: The Judge Emissary disappears from the Xene station, leaving much political uncertainty in its wake.</p><p>The Imposter: Someone is impersonating an Emissary: a mystic gone mad, someone lusting for wealth and power, or a Nazareem’s Sacrifice cell setting a trap for the PCs.</p>","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"","flags":{"yzecoriolis":{"customJournal":true},"coriolis-emissarylost":{"importPath":"Table/RollTables"}},"img":"","results":[{"_id":"cfcd208495d565ef","type":0,"weight":1,"range":[11,14],"text":" <b>ICON</b>: The Messenger* <br/> <b>KNOWN AS</b>: Nabi-mu-Qad <br/> <b>SYMMETRY MYSTIC</b>: Urni en-Argonnas <br/> <b>HOST BODY</b>: Alam Dania, Mira <br/>"},{"_id":"c4ca4238a0b92382","type":0,"weight":1,"range":[15,16],"text":" <b>ICON</b>: The Judge <br/> <b>KNOWN AS</b>: Hukim-mu-Qad <br/> <b>SYMMETRY MYSTIC</b>: Unknown ** <br/> <b>HOST BODY</b>: Yorûg om-Khalil, Altai <br/>"},{"_id":"c81e728d9d4c2f63","type":0,"weight":1,"range":[21,26],"text":" <b>ICON</b>: The Dancer <br/> <b>KNOWN AS</b>: Kama-mu-Qad <br/> <b>SYMMETRY MYSTIC</b>: Aisha en-Barka <br/> <b>HOST BODY</b>: Harish Verma, Mira <br/>"},{"_id":"eccbc87e4b5ce2fe","type":0,"weight":1,"range":[31,36],"text":" <b>ICON</b>: The Merchant <br/> <b>KNOWN AS</b>: Karob-mu-Qad <br/> <b>SYMMETRY MYSTIC</b>: Hiam en-Lamra <br/> <b>HOST BODY</b>: Faisal Kham, Kua <br/>"},{"_id":"a87ff679a2f3e71d","type":0,"weight":1,"range":[41,46],"text":" <b>ICON</b>: The Faceless One <br/> <b>KNOWN AS</b>: Hane-mu-Qad <br/> <b>SYMMETRY MYSTIC</b>: Chera en-Megrina <br/> <b>HOST BODY</b>: Leila Hatami, Dabaran <br/>"},{"_id":"e4da3b7fbbce2345","type":0,"weight":1,"range":[51,66],"text":" <b>ICON</b>: False Emissary <br/> <b>KNOWN AS</b>: (choose one of the above) <br/> <b>SYMMETRY MYSTIC</b>: – <br/> 